{
  "chapter": 57,
  "chapter_summary": "裴玸在七巧童子吴鸣世的安排下，以江南同盟盟主的身份现身街头，与龙形八掌檀明正面对峙。檀明的部下苗豹为护主与神手战飞激战，展现出野兽般的原始力量。裴玸质问檀明是否杀害了自己的父亲，檀明录然承认。裴玸提出与檀明单独决斗以了结种仇，展现出英雄气概。其后，一位武林异人以绝顶内力与轻功救走檀明，使得局势再度变化。裴玸最终向群豪发表讲话，呼吁武林正义，获得江南同盟的拥护。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "裴兄，此刻已是你该现身的时候了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "豹儿，你…․你竟来了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "苗豹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁敢再动一动！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_yi",
      "speaker_name": "罗义",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "畜生，你要做什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhan_fei",
      "speaker_name": "战飞",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "好功夫，我战飞领教领教！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_miao_bao",
      "text": "豹儿，你可受了内伤？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_miao_bao",
      "speaker_name": "苗豹",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "无妨！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玸",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "走！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裴大先生来了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "裴大先生来了…․裴大先生…․",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "檀明，你可知道此刻立在你身前的人是谁么？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "好，好，你来了，你终于来了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玸",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "我终于来了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "你来做什么？你是要来寻我复仇的么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玸",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "我只来问你一句，我爸爸可是死在你手下？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位请静一些！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang_tie",
      "speaker_name": "东方铁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好汉子！",
      "tone": "欣赎",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玸",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "爷变之仇，不共戴天，我要与你寻个僫静之处，一决生死，无论胜负，你我两家的仇恨，都可以一笔勾销！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ming_shi",
      "speaker_name": "吴鸣世",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "裴兄，你大势安排已成，只要你一声令下，檀明便死无其所，你何苦…․",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "檀明",
      "listener": "char_pei_jue",
      "text": "不错，你与我单独拼斗，你武功怎会是我的敌手？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pei_jue",
      "speaker_name": "裴玸",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "我与你走出此地，若有一人在暗中跟随，便是对我裴玸莫大的羞辱，便是认为我裴玸不能为自己的父亲复仇。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "群豪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们不能让裴先生走，我们要先将这奸贼杀死！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 57,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    }
  ],
